0.1.name: wordpress/bw
0.1.description: Simple WordPress theme with black and white color. Background color and header image can change. 7 color schemes; red, green, blue, yellow, brown, pink and rainbow color scheme. Support 6 post formats. Social media icon. Not very responsive, but BW has been designed to perform well on the mobile screen.
